snippet.title: OP Presents - True Crime
snippet.description:
True Crime documentaries and videos featuring Police Interrogations, Interviews, Court Verdicts, Testimonies and other true crime related content.  Nobody seems to understand why most police stations have such poor audio and video equipment that seems to date from the 1960's...

One of the channel's focuses is on hearing from the accused or suspect themselves to get the stories from their point of view, fascinating stuff.
